PARTIES
& EVENTS
IN PEMBROKE PINES, FLORIDA
At Level Twentynine, we believe that the right setting, combined with the perfect food and impeccable service, can transform a gathering into a truly unforgettable event. That’s why we’re proud to offer our exceptional space and services for your next party or event.
EXPERIENCE THE DIFFERENCE
Our elegant and versatile venue is the perfect setting for any occasion, from corporate gatherings and weddings to birthday parties and anniversary celebrations. We offer a variety of private event spaces to fit your specific needs, from intimate dining rooms to grand ballrooms, and everything in between.
Our team of experienced event planners and culinary experts will work with you to create a customized menu that suits your tastes and preferences, and our attentive staff will ensure that every detail is taken care of, from setup to cleanup.
